short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Update Projection Lab account balances from Monarch Money

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: One click update of account balances from Monarch Money to Projection Lab to keep retirement planning accurate and up to date. This is a paid extension which works with Individual or Pro accounts in Projection Lab.
